description:
&lt;p&gt;Due to the success and expansion of this recently introduced service, exciting opportunities have arisen in our new Prescription Ordering Direct (POD) Centre which provides support to patients ordering repeat prescriptions. This position is a rewarding but challenging opportunity for the right candidate. You must be able to demonstrate excellent customer service and communication skills within a fast paced team environment. You will also need to be flexible, able to work under pressure and manage difficult calls in a polite and professional manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours can be flexible, and training will be provided at base site (Swindon or Devizes) with the option of flexible working from home. Relevant experience in a GP practice / pharmacy / healthcare setting is preferable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In order to be considered for this role, please ensure you clearly demonstrate your experience, in the Supporting Information section of your application form, by giving specific examples for the criteria within the person specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information about this post please contact Elizabeth Rushforth on elizabeth.rushforth@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that the interview will be held via Zoom&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BSW CCG offers the following benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support of a healthy and safe environment / secure building&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free and plentiful car parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible working policies / supportive approach to individual needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team working / matrix working&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnership forum to enable joint decision making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to development opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stretch assignments / shadowing opportunities across the local health &amp; social care community (ACS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Signed the charter of employers re Mindful Employer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Signed up for Swindon Carers Employer Award&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
